
* language *

Syntax:	language [<user>] <text_def_language>

	Write to all/<user> a text which can include the international
	language definitions:

	^<symbol><character>	will generate <symbol> on <character>
	_<symbol><character>	will generate <symbol> under <character>

	Examples:                            _
			^_a	to generate  a

			_,s	to generate  s
				             ,

			^ ^     to generate  ^ itself

			_ _     to generate  _ itself

See also: .say
